''H<U+00E4>meenmaa'' was delivered from the dock back to the Navy on 13 April 2007 and ''Uusimaa'', which had been under modernization since November 2006 at the [[Aker Yards]] dock in [[Rauma, Finland|Rauma]], was delivered on 26 October 2007. ''H<U+00E4>meenmaa'' and ''Uusimaa'' will be conducting sea trials on their new systems until the end of 2008, when operational readiness is achieved.<ref>[http://www.mil.fi/merivoimat/tiedotteet/3456.dsp www.mil.fi 26.10.2007]</ref>

